headline: PGIM Investments wins nine 2025 LSEG Lipper Fund Awards
summary: NEWARK, N.J., March 14, 2025--PGIM Investments has been honored with nine 2025 LSEG Lipper Fund Awards, in recognition of the firm’s investment excellence across several funds spanning multiple asset classes.
